item.title: Ferrari Graveyard: Video of 14 supercar pile-up in Japan
item.description:
Ferrari Graveyard: Video of 14 supercar pile-up in Japan
An outing of luxury sports car enthusiasts in Japan ended in an expensive freeway pileup - smashing a stunning eight Ferraris, a Lamborghini and two Mercedes. Police say they believe the accident Sunday was touched off when the driver of one of the Ferraris tried to change lanes and hit the median barrier. He spun across the freeway, and the other cars collided while trying to avoid hitting his car. RT on Twitter http://twitter.com/RT_com RT on Facebook http://www.facebook.com/RTnews
